This paper focuses on learning a model of system dynamics online, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY). The paper also uses Bayesian learning to obtain a distribution over the system dynamics, which is a machine learning technique (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses optimizing system behavior and ensuring safety, which are topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper uses a chance constraint, which is a technique commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE).
